    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in flawless shape\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and detailed regularly. You won't find a single scratch or ding on this beauty. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. Come check it out, you won't be disappointed!",
