      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom-ready condition. The exterior features the original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like gloss and zero imperfections, while the interior still retains that fresh, new-car scent with supple leather and unblemished trim. Mechanically, it is flawless; every service has been performed on schedule at certified dealerships, and we have the full documentation to prove it. It comes complete with both original keys, the owner's manual in its leather case, and even the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly maintained example that drives exactly as it did the day it left the lot.",
      "price": 46500.0,
