    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014seriously, you won't find a single scratch on it! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, always garage-kept and pampered. It drives like an absolute dream and still feels like it just rolled off the lot. If you're looking for total perfection, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
