    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, featuring the legendary 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double VANOS system. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach: the rod bearing service has been performed, the VANOS unit has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension maintains its factory-spec geometry with fresh bushings, providing the tactile steering feedback and neutral handling balance characteristic of the M-division's peak era. This is a turn-key, collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance and an immaculate undercarriage.",
